{"tid":2209302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生FB出不到文：乾脆永遠封咗我","createTime":"2020-09-19T14:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:36.000Z","uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2884db7d72c6a8f1f54d0494b3c0d4d8d53078b5","tid":2209302,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"黃秋生向來都鍾意在FB做分享，自8月底後卻見他少出post，反而轉場到Twitter暢所欲言，他今日在FB留言：「呢度真係九唔搭八，忽然又可以發佈，想唔懷疑佢封鎖我都唔得。我自己已經放唔到嘢好耐。全部別人管理。不過話時話，都冇佢咁好氣，儍人有乜好鬧，鬧佢你都儍埋一份。乾脆永遠封咗我喇，唔係我久唔久都會忍唔住講嘢㗎。」秋生不滿疑似被FB「禁聲」，今日出文後，網民即力撐：「你係我最值得欣賞嘅影帝，唔好唔發聲呀」、「久唔久踩下條紅線，佢久唔久着下燈，我哋睇得好開心」、「講多啲，去Twitter都好，國際線」。"},{"pid":"b2347740fef77d09218fe59182c92ae2d6093099","tid":2209302,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m_sl0iC0duQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm_sl0iC0duQ&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=eba81cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m_sl0iC0duQ</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起佢首飛機歌 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/12/133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif&h=25438751&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f655dc4716657bcda465a6f249ace42ecca08fad","tid":2209302,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"疑似被FB「封鎖」，樂得在Twitter開心share，秋生於9月13日有說過：「如果咁X多人犯法被捕，咁你就要諗吓，到底佢哋犯法？定你哋犯緊法啦。」早前有孕婦及兒童被警察濫捕，秋生也看不過眼，9月13日在Twitter留言：「我非常重視保護婦女及兒童。吓？影到你打女人打細路喎。我話我非常重視保護我屋企嘅婦女及兒童。」9月17日再在Twitter說：「今日教大家乜嘢叫唱衰，一件事原本係好嘅你先可以唱衰。相反，一件事原本係衰嘅你先可以唱好。」"},{"pid":"09896bde86dea5e7d8eb287c31820eefa24d56ba","tid":2209302,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kpXzDdKh_7lXdY5upF7fubWsE9U=/535x626/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T6B6JVMT4BF2VF4O3MM22S3KEA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkpXzDdKh_7lXdY5upF7fubWsE9U%3D%2F535x626%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT6B6JVMT4BF2VF4O3MM22S3KEA.JPG&h=f710807f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dP_ey5fWpLmi7czekjea-XUF1xA=/535x145/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YNDIHH3NXJHDVCNTFF65RBIQOA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdP_ey5fWpLmi7czekjea-XUF1xA%3D%2F535x145%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYNDIHH3NXJHDVCNTFF65RBIQOA.JPG&h=ff339d8d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}